Nollywood actress Regina Daniels has revealed why she does not want to ever give birth to a daughter. According to the billionaire wife, she has no desire for a daughter as she can’t handle replicating her attitude. The mother of one shared this via her Insta story as she posted a screenshot of an image that had the inscription; “If my daughter gets my attitude, I’m finished.” Corroborating the inscription, the actress went ahead to state that it’s the same reason she also doesn’t want to have a daughter. She wrote: “That’s why I don’t want one till I’m ready to retire.”